This effect is called the magic order, and it‚Äôs super easy to recreate in CapCut.
First, place your phone on a tripod, show your phone with the image on it, and place it on your glass. Then, hold your finger on your phone and pretend something is coming out of it.
For the second shot, grab a drink and pour it into the glass. Import both clips into CapCut and scroll to your second clip. Select it and make it an overlay.
Drag the overlay to the exact moment where you hold your finger on your phone. Select the overlay and go to Mask. Choose the Rectangle option and position the mask so it hides the glass.
To make it even better, add a vibration flash effect at the moment your finger touches the phone. Export your video, and it‚Äôs ready to share.
